narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: This course is probably a one-off, but if it is ever offered again, would recommend matroids. Subject matter leans mostly towards combinatorics and linear algebra, so if you like those, take this one. Max obviously put good work into designing the class, lectures, and problem sets.
Yeah, it was certainly interesting, and probably useful.
Yes. Matroids are a very interesting subject. Max is a great lecturer and you'll learn a lot.
